question: Tī siâu-khuán uán ê chiân thê-tâi chu-pāi kàu siâu-khuán uán ê sì tńg-sî, pau-kòat ê chióng-kim lóng-chóng sī siáⁿ-chē?
Na-lunn chit-ê khoat-mîng sī chhòan-siⁿ to̍k-tōa ê lōe-iông, chhù-sî ê siâⁿ-chè pí chu-liāu tē-it khóat-mîng ê siâⁿ-chè pí-chāi to̍k-tōa koh-khah to̍k-tōa?
Chiah's gı̂l-lúi bô-tiānn-á sin-lâi ê chiúⁿ-ke, mā-sī chū tò-piān ū sin-lâi ê chiúⁿ-ke ê āu-chi̍t ê gı̂l-lúi. Tī chiah's kóe-á gı̂l-lúi ê "Player of the Round" ê miâ-jī sī siáⁿ-mi̍h?
Lament ah Player of the Round bat bat bat teh 2009 hit tiam e lam-mi?
Tī chit ê tournament tùi qualifying rounds kàu proper rounds ê kòe-têng tiong, sin jīm ê sò͘-liōng ê kuán-chè ū siám-mi chhián-chhiat ê tōng-thâu?
answer: Chit ê tournament ê chho͘-téng sî (Extra Preliminary Round) sin jīm ê sò͘-liōng siōng chē (406), liáu-āu ē chiām-chiām kiám-chió chāi āu-piah ê qualifying rounds. Kàu 'Proper' rounds khai-sí ê sî, First kap Third rounds ū chin tōa ê sin jīm (sī 48 kap 44, tùi-tâng), chi̍t-kóa 'Proper' rounds iā bô sin jīm. Che sī piáu-bīn ū chi̍t khoán hun-chàn ê jīm-chè, koan-hē ki-chū tùi i ê pâi-chí lâi jīm.

question: Tī tsuân tio̍h tsuân-tāi (tùi Extra Preliminary Round kàu Semi-Finals) ê tsuân-pōo tsuat-tiûnn sò͘-liōng tiong, ū sîn-me phiah ê phiah-tāi sī chāi tsuán-ka tsuat-tiûnn (tùi Extra Preliminary kàu Fourth Round Qualifying) sī tú-tio̍h ê?

Tī 'Third Round Proper' ê só͘-chāi tiāⁿ-chē ê só͘-chāi sòaⁿ sī 32, nā-sī tiāⁿ-chē sī 25, án-ni chū chi̍t-ê sûn-chāi tńg-lâi liáu-āu, lán thang kiám-chiâⁿ ū nn̄g-ê kiû-tūi chìuⁿ chāi tòa-té, nā-sī tòa-té ê kiû-tūi tiāⁿ-chē ū chāi tòa-té, ū nn̄g-ê tiāⁿ-chē sī 25, ná-sī 32, chiū-án-ni lâi kiám-chiâⁿ ū nn̄g-ê kiû-tūi sìu liáu chāi tòa-té?

Tī chit ê tē-iâⁿ-chhia lū-chîng, ē-sái liáu-kái kóng tē-iâⁿ-chhia ê lū-chîng kap pôaⁿ-siâⁿ ê kim-á ū ti̍t-chiap ê koan-hē bē? (Tī chit ê tē-iâⁿ-chhia lū-chîng, ē-sái liáu-kái kóng tē-iâⁿ-chhia ê lū-chîng kap pôaⁿ-siâⁿ ê kim-á ū ti̍t-chiap ê koan-hē bē?)
answer: Ū, sī ū chiok kiông ê chi̍t ê positive correlation. Chhin-chhiūⁿ, tòe-koh thàu-chhoan ê lū-chîng ti̍h-ài kiâⁿ kah āu-piah ê lū-chîng (chhin-chhiūⁿ, tùi 'Preliminary' kàu 'Semi-Finals'), pôaⁿ-siâⁿ ê kim-á tō koh koh khah chē. Pí-lē kóng, Extra Preliminary Round ê pôaⁿ-siâⁿ sī £750, chiūⁿ chiâⁿ kah Fourth Round Qualifying ê sî sī £12,500, chiâⁿ kah Semi-Finals ê chiâⁿ-chiáⁿ sī £1,000,000. Chit ê kò͘-chō chiok ū hō͘ sài-só͘ tī thòe-bóe ê kai-tōaⁿ teh chiâⁿ-chiáⁿ ê sî koh koh teh chin chiap ê hō͘-chì.

question: Tī só͘-chāi ê chu-liāu tiong, kin-á-hōe 'Round' ê tiâu-bûn, "Player of the Round" ê chióng-miâ bē-tàng sú-iōng, che sī ūi-tio̍h kiám-miâ?
Gim-kènn-ê kim-koaⁿ-ê cēnn-choē cēnn-choē cēnn-choē cēnn-choē, kā Pài-tue̍h-tiâⁿ ê iâⁿ-chiáⁿ kim-koaⁿ chòe phó͘-chū?
answer: Between Sixth Round Proper and Semi-Finals

question: Chiu-siu ê kim-chiân, tùi chhù-piⁿ kah chhù-piⁿ ê kòe-têng lâi kóng, ū siáⁿ-chē piàn-hòa?
answer: Tī chhù-piⁿ chin-hêng ê sî, chiu-siu kim-chiân to̍h chin-chiàⁿ teh cheng-ka, che sī thàm-chhoē chòe-oân-á kiat-sûn kap khùn-lân chha-put-to it-poaⁿ, kah kiat-sûn ê tūi-ngá chin chiap.
